  dsimp [Topology.P2]
  intro x _
  have hEq : closure A = (Set.univ : Set X) := by
    simpa using hDense.closure_eq
  have : x ∈ (Set.univ : Set X) := by

  simpa [hEq, interior_univ, closure_univ] using this
